6
00:00:31,020 --> 00:00:34,840
We can find a place where no one knows us.

7
00:00:35,060 --> 00:00:38,040
Wouldn't it be nice to live a simple and peaceful life?

8
00:00:39,380 --> 00:00:40,200
No.

9
00:00:41,100 --> 00:00:44,360
What I want is power and status.

10
00:00:44,800 --> 00:00:47,120
If you're willing to help me, then stay.

11
00:00:47,140 --> 00:00:48,160
If not,

12
00:00:49,180 --> 00:00:50,080
get out.

13
00:00:58,960 --> 00:01:00,560
To bring down Yi Qiuting,

14
00:01:00,830 --> 00:01:02,360
we can only do it through Zhao Xingrou.

15
00:01:02,740 --> 00:01:04,440
There's someone who can help us.

16
00:01:06,610 --> 00:01:07,360
Who?

17
00:01:08,880 --> 00:01:09,880
Leng Mei.

18
00:01:12,210 --> 00:01:13,900
Since you've already placed someone

19
00:01:13,930 --> 00:01:15,520
close to Zhao Xingrou,

20
00:01:15,980 --> 00:01:17,600
why haven't you killed her yet?

21
00:01:17,820 --> 00:01:18,960
I'm not like you,

22
00:01:19,190 --> 00:01:21,320
competing with a woman for a man.

23
00:01:21,730 --> 00:01:23,530
Killing Zhao Xingrou

24
00:01:23,550 --> 00:01:24,760
would bring me no benefit.

25
00:01:25,360 --> 00:01:29,880
Keeping her alive is to use her against Yi Qiuting.

26
00:01:29,930 --> 00:01:35,700
[Blazing Elegance]

27
